    "20 ADVANCING WASHING TONS INTERESTS STOCK MARKET SIW BUT DULL Typical Midsummer Conditions Prevail With Small v Transactions X By H J DUIZEND Copyright 1923 by Cosmopolitan News Service NEW YORK Aug 11Typical midsummer conditions prevailed in the stock market today The short ness of the session sandwiched be tween yesterdays suspension and the regular weekend recess was not at all conducive to operations on either side of the market Still in spite of a few weak spots crop ping up in some parts of the list the tone was one of steadiness al though the smallness of the trans actions precluded any indication as to the course of values in the im mediate future i With the attend ance on the floor extremely light there was no disposition among traders to take a definite stand until next week when it is ex pected development in the domestic and foreign situation which were overlooked during the period of national mourning will receive closer consideration A good deal of attention was paid to the movements in the rubber atd tire shares in connection with re ports of overproduction and of an impending cut in prices Bearish activities were centered in United"
